name: Gochujang Chicken Wings
description: 10 sweet, salty, spicy, crispy, and messy wings covered with gochujang, sweet BBQ, and sesame seeds served with a side of blue cheese or ranch.

name: Half Order Gochujang Wings
description: Six sweet, salty, spicy, crispy, and messy wings covered with gochujang, sweet BBQ, and sesame seeds served with a side of blue cheese or ranch.

name: Everything Bagel Edamame
description: Lightly steamed and covered in everything bagel seasoning.

name: Boneless Gochujang Wings
description: A pound of sweet, salty, crispy, and messy boneless wings covered with a house made gochujang sauce. Served with a side of blue cheese or ranch.

name: Vegetable Spring Rolls
description: Three hefty spring rolls filled with a blend of mixed veggies and wrapped in a thin spring roll and deep fried until golden brown, served with a sweet chili sauce.

name: Miso Ramen
description: Chicken and pork broth, blend of 4 types of miso, chicken katsu, soy egg, menma, green onions, corn, roasted sesame seeds and a pad of butter.

name: Tan Tan Ramen
description: Chicken and pork broth, browned and seasoned ground pork, sesame paste, ginger, chili oil, green onions, bean sprouts and garlic.

name: Kimchi Ramen
description: Spicy Chicken and Pork broth, miso, gochujang, kimchi, roasted sesame seeds, soy egg, soy tofu, corn, chashu, green onion and some heat.

name: Shoyu Ramen
description: Clear chicken broth, blend of premium soy sauces and umami packed bonito, chasu, menma, wood ear mushrooms, green onions, roasted sesame seeds and soy egg.

name: Vegan Kimchi Ramen
description: Vegan. Spicy. Vegetable broth, miso, gochujang, vegan kimchi, soy tofu, corn, menma, roasted sesame seeds, and some heat.

name: Vegan Tan Tan Ramen
description: Vegan. Thick vegetable broth, fried tofu, sesame paste, ginger, chive oil, green onions, roasted sesame seeds and garlic.

name: Vegetarian Miso Ramen
description: Vegetarian. Thick vegetable broth, blend of 4 types of miso, soy egg, fried tofu, menma, green onions, roasted sesame seeds, corn and a pad of butter.

name: Katsu Loco Moco
description: White rice, chicken katsu, brown gravy and a fried egg all playing on a traditional Hawaiian staple.

name: Ground Pork Rice Bowl
description: White rice, ground pork, kimchi, green onions and bean sprouts with a special sauce.

name: Fried Tofu Rice Bowl
description: White rice, fried tofu, vegan kimchi, corn, green onions and bean sprouts with a special vegan sauce.

name: Pork Belly Rice Bowl
description: White rice, thick cut pork belly, corn, bean sprouts, kimchi, and green onion drizzled with a special sweet and savory sauce.

name: Chocolate Cake
description: A deliciously moist fudge cake with a rich chocolate fudge icing and chocolate crunch coating around the sides.

name: Fried Cheesecake
description: Basically a cheesecake burrito fried, covered in powdered sugar and served with a side of your choice of dessert sauce.

name: Chocolate Brownie
description: Super rich and thick, and Drizzled with Chocolate syrup. It's hard not to eat all of these ourselves!
